    "type": "message",
    "text": "Iterating towards formalization in a dialogue sounds just right for EUP. But is GPT-4 up to it? It requires a lot of short-term memory, to hold the entire conversation. Plus a decent competence in formalization, which GPT-4 may or may not have picked up from its text corpus (which is the main unknown for all of us who don't work for OpenAI).",
